data.description: Welcome to this charming 4 bed, 2 bath home in the quiet and neighborly Baird Creek neighborhood! Step inside to discover new vinyl flooring throughout all four bedrooms, offering a modern and easy-to-maintain touch. The finished basement is a versatile haven, boasting a spacious family room with an electric fireplace for cozy evenings. A bedroom with a walk-in closet, two bonus rooms, and a convenient wet bar complete the lower level, providing ample space for entertainment or relaxation. Nearby schools just a leisurely stroll away. The fenced-in yard ensures privacy, featuring an in-ground firepit, perfect for gatherings and making memories. Don't miss the chance to call this welcoming residence your home- schedule your showing today!
